RSC LaTeX template files
========================

The following files in this directory are part of the Royal Society of
Chemistry article ("Paper") LaTeX template, distributed by the RSC for
authors preparing journal submissions, and are vendored unchanged so that
authors can build a Digital Discovery (RSC) style submission without
downloading the template separately:

    rsc.bst
    rsc.bib
    headers/CH.{eps,pdf}
    headers/LH.{eps,pdf}
    headers/RH.{eps,pdf}
    headers/LF.{eps,pdf}
    headers/RF.{eps,pdf}

Copyright (c) The Royal Society of Chemistry. These files are not
relicensed by this repository; they remain subject to the terms under
which the RSC distributes its journal template.

The manuscript source (`main.tex`) is original to this project.

Other LaTeX packages required by `main.tex` (e.g. `mhchem`, `balance`,
`caption`, `fancyhdr`, `lipsum`, `natbib`, `lastpage`, `times`,
`mathptmx`, `url`, `extsizes`) are expected to be supplied by the local TeX
distribution (e.g. TeX Live's `texlive-latex-recommended`,
`texlive-latex-extra`, `texlive-science`, `texlive-fonts-recommended`).
They are deliberately NOT vendored here so that this repository does not
redistribute third-party packages outside the terms of their upstream
licenses.
